data.description:
Adorable Mother in Law Apartment with new paint, flooring and in-unit Washer/Dryer. The unit also has its own backyard with a private deck. Wonderful neighborhood within walking distance to Kopachuck State Park. Max of 2 People.

Owner pays for water, cable, internet, garbage. Renter responsible for power. No smoking permitted. One small dog negotiable with additional fee. Security deposit, first and last month rent all due at signing.
